                <p>      			
                    I<hi rend="grantha">n-nṛ</hi>t=ta-maṇṭapam
                    <lb n="2"/>tiru-<unclear>k</unclear> <gap reason="illegible" quantity="2" unit="character"/> ttuvittār tiru
